all of the above accusations

280
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,679
are supported by video evidence.

281
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:53,999
We can continue playing the footage.

282
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,519
What's there to play?

283
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:57,200
Defendant, maintain courtroom decorum.

284
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:59,879
No, sorry, Your Honor.

285
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:00,559
My...

286
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:02,199
That's just my temper.

287
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,719
It's out of frustration,

288
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,079
wanting the best for the child.

289
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,599
What parent disciplines a child

290
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,199
without laying a finger on them?

291
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,879
And Liu Wenbo,

292
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:12,039
he says I abuse the child?

293
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,319
If I go back and check the recordings,

294
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,339
I can find plenty of videos

295
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:15,639
of him abusing the child too.

296
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:17,280
You also abuse the child.

297
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,600
Continue with the next video.

298
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:26,720
Push harder.

299
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,039
Put some strength into it.

300
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:31,759
We have a structured program.

301
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:32,479
Move back a bit.

302
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:34,439
This will harm the child's body.

303
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,799
Xiaolongbao's mom, you can't do this.

304
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:37,960
Our program progresses step by step.

305
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,000
Come on, push harder.

306
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:43,559
This will harm the child's body.

307
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:44,680
Stop.

308
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,200
Look at this.

309
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:48,769
Everyone, take a look.

310
00:11:48,770 --> 00:11:50,990
This is how Sun Lala abuses my daughter.

311
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,720
My daughter is so pitiful.

312
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,040
She's really too pitiful.

313
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:56,840
Plaintiff,

314
00:11:57,170 --> 00:11:58,399
there's something

315
