336
00:12:52,630 --> 00:12:54,880
We have to discipline them, right?

337
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:56,399
As an ordinary person,

338
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,799
I can't always tell

339
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,149
