Go on, keep making things up.

344
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:11,560
Lying through your teeth.

345
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,040
Defendant, maintain order.
Do not interrupt.

346
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,519
You've all seen it.

347
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:16,999
With Sun Lala's personality,

348
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,919
