351
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,759
All these years,
I've been suppressed by her.

352
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,520
I've lost count of how many times
I've endured her.

353
00:13:25,590 --> 00:13:26,679
That's complete nonsense.

354
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:28,279
So you're saying
