That is clearly a man's hand.

362
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:48,960
So what if it's a man's hand?

363
00:13:49,640 --> 00:13:51,000
There are plenty of men.

364
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,430
Well then,

365
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:53,399
