367
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:56,760
Yes, ask me. That man is him.

368
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:58,200
Him, that's his hand.

369
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,640
Plaintiff,

370
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,120
I remind you,

371
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:07,120
