372
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,440
carries legal consequences.

373
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:13,240
I can also prove

374
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:15,719
that he was the one filming this video.

375
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,920
The cameraman.

376
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,079
(A helpless child)

377
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:20,799
(being treated as property
in the internet age.)

378
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:22,079
(The selfish parents)

379
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:24,640
(calculating their value
down to every last detail.)

380
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,959
(These parents)

381
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:28,719
(have long forgotten that
when a life comes into this world,)

382
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,400
(into a family,)

383
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:33,640
(it already becomes
part of their own lives.)

384
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:36,350
(But those consumed by desire,)

385
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:38,879
(can they no longer see)

386
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:41,639
(the bond of flesh and blood.)

387
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:43,399
The two of you,

388
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:43,919
how can you lie

389
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,579
