Liu Wenbo, come here.

394
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,239
Ms. Qin, what's wrong?

395
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,359
Why are you so angry?

396
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,679
Why didn't you tell me

397
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:17,760
