398
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:20,720
Telling you something
that clearly doesn't help me, why would I?

399
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:22,360
Besides, you said
one person was restraining her,

400
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,559
then naturally
someone had to be filming,

401
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:25,039
right?

402
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:27,560
I didn't expect
that as the child's father,

403
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:28,999
