406
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,960
I thought that was a cameraman.

407
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,269
Of course, it could've been him.

408
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:36,679
And I was telling the truth.

409
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:38,719
I was only there a few times,
just a handful of times.

410
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,760
What's the difference
between once and ten times?

411
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,399
Why are you yelling at me?

412
