those two female judges.

422
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:03,880
I did exactly what you said.

423
00:16:03,880 --> 00:16:05,839
Now think of another solution for me.
As long as I get custody of the child...

424
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:06,959
