- Get ready.

436
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,399
Put the child down.

437
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,479
Stop filming.

438
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:38,319
Sweetheart, come to Daddy.

439
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:41,199
- The judge hasn't ruled yet.
- Are you trying to start something?

440
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,399
Move aside. What are you filming?

441
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:44,039
Exactly, the judge hasn't ruled yet.

442
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:45,840
But when it does,
the child will definitely be mine.

443
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:46,439
Before that,

444
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,879
