446
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:49,359
Move aside. Come here.

447
00:16:49,360 --> 00:16:50,599
What are you doing?

448
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,239
Move aside.

449
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:53,799
