450
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:56,199
I'm a man. If you hit me, you'd better
think about who's at a disadvantage.

451
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:58,719
Liu Wenbo, who told you to cause trouble
at the courthouse?

452
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:00,799
Aren't you handling my case anymore?
I'll handle it myself.

453
00:17:00,800 --> 00:17:02,520
Don't use force.

454
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,639
- What are you doing?
- Don't use force.

455
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:05,920
Don't use force.

456
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:09,319
Liu Wenbo.

457
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:10,039
What are you doing?

458
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:11,360
Move.

459
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,799
Liu Wenbo.

460
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,999
Let go of me.

461
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,000
What are you doing?

462
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:48,719
Let go.

463
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,480
Stop.

464
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,399
Let go. Is the child not your own?

465
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,600
Let go.

466
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:56,639
Xiaolongbao.

467
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:57,839
Are you okay, Xiaolongbao?

468
00:17:57,840 --> 00:17:58,839
Come here.

469
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:00,359
The child is already in pain.

470
00:18:00,360 --> 00:18:01,839
Can't you feel it?

471
00:18:01,840 --> 00:18:04,200
He started it first.

472
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:05,439
Your Honors,

473
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:07,669
