479
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:16,960
Mommy's here too.

480
00:18:25,970 --> 00:18:27,679
I'm telling you,
the tone needs to change.

481
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:29,069
We need to move fast.

482
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:29,879
I'm telling you,

483
