495
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:51,040
Look.

496
00:18:51,580 --> 00:18:52,999
(Where is the sense of parental responsibility?
Doesn't the child's growth matter?)

497
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:53,920
(It's really hard on the child,)
This.

498
00:18:54,150 --> 00:18:55,040
