507
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:10,759
Alright.

508
00:19:10,760 --> 00:19:12,720
Oh no, the live stream got banned.

509
00:19:13,570 --> 00:19:14,420
I...

510
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:17,679
(Login restricted, cannot be restored)

511
