534
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:01,650
No way it can be withdrawn.

535
00:20:03,560 --> 00:20:04,119
Alright.

536
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:05,719
Then send me an address,

537
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:06,960
I'll head over right now.

538
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,180
Okay.

539
00:20:09,040 --> 00:20:11,079
Why are you still standing there?
Get in the car.

540
00:20:11,080 --> 00:20:12,240
Hurry up.

541
00:20:13,250 --> 00:20:15,029
Where are we going?
The hearing is about to start.

542
00:20:15,030 --> 00:20:15,879
What hearing?

543
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:18,200
At a time like this, the account's gone.

544
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:19,369
If I can't get it back,

545
00:20:19,370 --> 00:20:21,160
am I supposed to live off nothing?

546
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:23,360
Stop standing there, drive.

547
00:20:23,970 --> 00:20:26,920
My eight hundred thousand.

548
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,279
Hello, excuse me,
where is the children's room?

549
00:20:36,280 --> 00:20:37,600
Turn right ahead.

550
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:39,440
Thank you.

551
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:44,839
Judge Yu, hello.

552
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:46,999
Sorry, the child
forgot her water bottle.

553
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:49,000
Xiaolongbao, whose bottle is this?

554
00:20:49,040 --> 00:20:50,960
Let me put it here for you, okay?

555
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:53,040
Ms. Qin,

556
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:54,520
where is your client?

557
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:57,280
I... I'm not sure.

558
00:20:57,600 --> 00:20:59,719
I'm no longer
representing him in this case.

559
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:00,959
Then where is he?

560
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,679
Someone has to take care
of the child, right?

561
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:04,520
He's not coming?
He doesn't want the child anymore?

562
00:21:04,540 --> 00:21:05,759
Do you mean

563
00:21:05,760 --> 00:21:07,400
her mother has agreed,

564
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:09,999
or that the panel has already decided

565
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,440
to award custody to the father?

566
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:12,719
Alright.

567
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,720
I'll call Liu Wenbo right away.

568
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:18,799
What's wrong?

569
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:19,719
Liu Wenbo,

570
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:21,239
come to the children's room now.

571
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,239
Xiaolongbao is here.

572
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,720
Come pick her up.

573
00:21:25,020 --> 00:21:26,639
Now that the account is banned,
she pushed daughter to me?

574
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,750
She wishes.

575
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:28,810
You...

576
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,559
He's not coming?

577
00:21:33,560 --> 00:21:34,800
He doesn't want the child anymore?

578
00:21:36,120 --> 00:21:37,280
He

579
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,360
probably

580
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:42,400
won't make it.

581
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:46,800
I want Mom.

582
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:55,520
Okay. Thank you for your help.

583
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,760
We can't reach her.

584
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:01,599
The studio has been locked up
for several days now.

585
00:22:01,600 --> 00:22:02,999
Apparently, once the lawsuit started,

586
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,959
Sun Lala had already applied
to terminate the lease.

587
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,839
And the property management

588
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:07,720
doesn't have
any other contact information.

589
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,010
Alright.

590
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:12,860
Thank you.

591
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,360
Sorry for the trouble.

592
00:22:14,920 --> 00:22:16,840
We called the property management
at Liu Wenbo's place.

593
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:18,159
They knocked,

594
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,119
but no one answered.

595
00:22:19,120 --> 00:22:21,320
They said he often stays away for days.

596
00:22:21,600 --> 00:22:24,600
Last time there was a leak at home,
it also took several days to reach him.

597
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:27,159
What kind of people are they?

598
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:28,239
One moment,

599
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,479
they're at each other's throats,

600
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:31,839
acting like they'll tear
the child apart,

601
00:22:31,840 --> 00:22:32,960
and the next moment,

602
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:34,239
they both disappear.

603
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:35,920
Gone without a trace.

604
00:22:39,320 --> 00:22:40,680
Look at this.

605
00:22:40,840 --> 00:22:41,920
(Parents fighting violently outside court)
The whole internet

606
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,040
(sparks public outrage)
is condemning them.

607
00:22:43,120 --> 00:22:45,720
Saying they were exploiting
their daughter for money.

608
00:22:46,120 --> 00:22:48,429
Sun Lala's live stream and account
have also been banned.

609
00:22:48,430 --> 00:22:49,479
They probably think

610
00:22:49,480 --> 00:22:51,560
the child is no longer useful.

611
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,559
Given the current public opinion,

612
00:22:53,560 --> 00:22:55,760
even if the account is recovered,
it won't help much.

613
00:22:56,360 --> 00:22:57,919
They forced
the child into live streaming,

614
00:22:57,920 --> 00:22:59,439
and the audience
won't accept it anymore.

615
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:00,720
What do you mean?

616
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:02,560
Are you saying

617
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:05,160
no one will want this child anymore?

618
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,599
Who knows how they think.

619
00:23:07,600 --> 00:23:09,239
But right now, the most urgent issue

620
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:11,000
is what to do with the child tonight.

621
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:16,799
If nothing else,

622
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:18,319
I can take her home.

623
00:23:18,320 --> 00:23:19,600
No.

624
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:23,159
Even if there's nowhere else,
she can't go to your place.

625
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:25,960
Fei just recovered
and can't handle any stress.

626
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:28,760
Don't bring strangers home all the time.

627
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:31,320
What stranger? She's just a child.

628
00:23:31,360 --> 00:23:33,360
The child is fine,

629
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:35,879
but those two parents are the problem.

630
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:36,719
You never know

631
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:39,120
what trouble they might stir up later.

632
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:45,640
What about the plaintiff's lawyer?

633
00:23:45,800 --> 00:23:47,959
Can she help think of a solution?

634
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:49,119
No.

635
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:50,840
I already asked.

636
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:53,639
Ms. Qin said her home is in the suburbs.

637
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:55,760
I know that place, it's too far.

638
00:23:55,840 --> 00:23:57,759
Besides, it's not realistic
for her to take the child.

639
00:23:57,760 --> 00:24:00,359
More importantly,
the child was left at the court,

640
00:24:00,360 --> 00:24:02,240
not at her law firm.

641
00:24:06,280 --> 00:24:07,359
Alright then,

642
00:24:07,360 --> 00:24:09,119
I'll take the child home tonight.

643
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:11,919
Perfect timing,
my mother-in-law will love her.

644
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:13,439
Saves her from nagging me

645
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,880
about having a grandchild.

646
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:18,720
Let me show you a magic trick.

647
00:24:19,040 --> 00:24:21,279
Look, so many little rocking horses,
aren't they cute?

648
00:24:21,280 --> 00:24:22,720
I will ride one for you.

649
00:24:24,040 --> 00:24:25,360
Giddy up.

650
00:24:26,040 --> 00:24:27,840
What made that sound?

651
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,360
Ran over a chicken.

652
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,880
Try making the sound.

653
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:39,400
See if you can hit it.

654
00:24:42,320 --> 00:24:44,160
You got one, right?

655
00:24:44,280 --> 00:24:45,079
Here,

656
00:24:45,080 --> 00:24:46,800
Xiaolongbao, give it a try.

657
00:24:48,560 --> 00:24:50,200
Still unhappy?

658
00:24:54,520 --> 00:24:56,080
Tell me,

659
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:58,440
are you hungry, thirsty, or

660
00:24:58,840 --> 00:25:00,400
do you need the bathroom?

661
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:04,800
Xiaolongbao.

662
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:07,640
I'm back.

663
00:25:08,760 --> 00:25:10,120
Xiaolongbao.

664
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:12,719
I just called your mom.

665
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:15,239
She said she'll be working late today,

666
00:25:15,240 --> 00:25:17,680
not sure when she'll be back.

667
00:25:17,840 --> 00:25:19,399
How about this,

668
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:22,600
come home with me tonight, okay?

669
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,559
At my place,

670
00:25:24,560 --> 00:25:27,119
there's a swing, rocking horses.

671
00:25:27,120 --> 00:25:28,559
Lots of kids don't want to leave

672
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:30,319
once they come.

673
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:31,879
Do you want to go?

674
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:32,679
Let's go,

675
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:35,320
come take a look, alright?

676
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:39,799
What's wrong?

677
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:41,039
Let me hold you.

678
00:25:41,040 --> 00:25:42,880
Let me hold you.

679
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:45,679
What's wrong?

680
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,319
Le.

681
00:25:46,320 --> 00:25:47,319
Quick, put Xiaolongbao down.

682
00:25:47,320 --> 00:25:48,079
What's wrong?

683
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:49,199
Come, Xiaolongbao.

684
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,599
Are you okay, Judge Yu?

685
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:51,359
- Le.
- What happened?

686
00:25:51,360 --> 00:25:51,879
What's wrong?

687
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,879
Slowly, get up.

688
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:55,320
Where does it hurt?

689
00:25:57,600 --> 00:25:58,960
Blood.

690
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:00,200
Why...

691
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:01,960
Why is there bleeding?

692
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:07,590
Careful.

693
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:09,680
Slow down.

694
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,199
Stay with Le.

695
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:12,439
Keep me updated if anything happens.

696
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:13,340
Okay.

697
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:21,719
Don't worry, Le will be fine.

698
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:23,359
Keep trying to contact the parents,

699
00:26:23,360 --> 00:26:24,759
or see if there are other relatives

700
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:26,200
who can take her.

701
00:26:27,600 --> 00:26:30,039
(Fei low activity mode)
Why is Fei still at Forest Park so late?

702
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:31,960
Why hasn't her dad picked her up?

703
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:32,919
(Call Yongjiu)

704
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:33,600
(Yongjiu dialing)

705
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:38,199
Hello,

706
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:41,079
the number you dialed
cannot be reached at the moment.

707
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:42,160
This is bad.

708
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:44,200
(Lian Mutton Soup)

709
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:49,679
Hello, Lian Mutton Soup.

710
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:50,839
This is Fei's mom.

711
00:26:50,840 --> 00:26:52,160
Is Lian Yongjiu there?

712
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:52,879
Jing,

713
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:55,919
the boss went to the northern
cold storage to pick up goods.

714
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,119
Then where is Fei?

715
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:58,559
Is she at the shop?

716
00:26:58,560 --> 00:27:00,200
Fei isn't here.

717
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:01,920
Thank you.

718
00:27:02,360 --> 00:27:03,600
What's wrong?

719
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,079
Ms. Xia,

720
00:27:08,080 --> 00:27:09,719
has the spring outing ended?

721
00:27:09,720 --> 00:27:10,999
Have they all returned to school?

722
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,799
The activity ended at 2:30.

723
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:15,480
The bus got back around 3:30.

724
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:16,759
Then Fei's dad,

725
00:27:16,760 --> 00:27:17,959
did he pick her up?

726
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,599
I'm not sure.

727
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:20,719
I'm sick today,

728
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:22,720
so the PE teacher took the class.

729
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,159
But he told me

730
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,959
all the children had been picked up.

731
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,040
Thank you.

732
00:27:31,280 --> 00:27:32,119
I have to go.

733
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:32,959
I need to find Fei.

734
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:34,519
Do you want me to go with you?

735
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:36,520
No, you stay with Xiaolongbao.

736
00:27:37,800 --> 00:27:42,759
(Children's Room)

737
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:44,040
Judge Shen,

738
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:45,999
how is Judge Yu?

739
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:46,960
She...

740
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:50,280
Could it be a miscarriage?

741
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:52,240
It's still unclear.

742
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:54,480
Why are you alone?
Where is everyone else?

743
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,889
Who are you expecting?

744
00:27:56,890 --> 00:27:59,600
Shouldn't there at least be a woman here
to take care of her?

745
00:28:01,360 --> 00:28:02,279
Chief Judge Shu,

746
00:28:02,280 --> 00:28:04,720
or that female clerk from earlier.

747
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:08,720
Ms. Shu had something come up and left.

748
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,439
That young woman

749
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,360
went to the hospital together.

750
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:15,399
Alright, then hurry and find someone.

751
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:17,079
Anyone from another division is fine.

752
00:28:17,080 --> 00:28:17,959
I have a client waiting,

753
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:19,079
I'm already half an hour late.

754
00:28:19,080 --> 00:28:20,060
I'm leaving.

755
00:28:20,600 --> 00:28:21,840
Where are you going?

756
00:28:22,360 --> 00:28:23,919
This is your case,

757
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:26,720
your client, your party.

758
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:29,520
If you leave, what about Xiaolongbao?

759
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:30,959
No,

760
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,719
I'm no longer handling this case.

761
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,320
Don't push the child onto me.

762
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:35,519
Listen,

763
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:37,639
Liu Wenbo only paid me
a three hundred deposit.

764
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:39,079
I've already agreed to refund it.

765
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:40,639
On top of that,
travel and phone expenses,

766
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:42,359
I've even spent on
three large cappuccinos.

767
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:43,919
I thought if I won this case,

768
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,480
maybe I could get reimbursed.

769
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,800
But given how things are now,

770
00:28:47,960 --> 00:28:50,159
whether I win
or not makes no difference.

771
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,319
No one's reimbursing me.

772
00:28:51,320 --> 00:28:52,440
Wait.

773
00:28:53,320 --> 00:28:55,079
I'm the judge on this case,

774
00:28:55,080 --> 00:28:56,880
you're the lawyer.

775
00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:58,560
With things like this happening,

776
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:00,079
shouldn't we work together

777
00:29:00,080 --> 00:29:01,079
to find a solution?

778
00:29:01,080 --> 00:29:02,520
How?

779
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:03,999
We've called,

780
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:05,800
no one answers at home or the studio.

781
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:08,110
I can't go searching the streets.

782
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:10,479
Doesn't Xiaolongbao have a grandmother?

783
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:11,919
Did Liu Wenbo ever mention her?

784
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:13,199
Do you have a number?

785
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:14,400
No number,

786
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:19,839
but I remember once when I went to
get him to sign something,

787
00:29:19,840 --> 00:29:21,959
we met at a teahouse in Jinshuli.

788
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:23,719
He pointed and said

789
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:26,160
his mother lived
in the complex across the street.

790
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:28,519
If I remember correctly,

791
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:30,040
it should be

792
00:29:30,080 --> 00:29:31,360
the seventeenth floor.

793
00:29:34,560 --> 00:29:35,519
Sorry,

794
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:38,199
the number you dialed cannot be reached.

795
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,759
Please try again later.

796
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:41,800
(Bluetooth call Yongjiu)

797
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:46,720
Come in.

798
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:48,710
Mr. He.

799
00:29:48,830 --> 00:29:49,720
Shen.

800
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:52,359
Let me brief you.

801
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:53,920
About Ms. Shu and Le...

802
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:55,599
I already know.

803
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:57,560
Danian just told me.

804
00:29:58,240 --> 00:30:00,320
Trouble never comes alone.

805
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,679
Is the child alright?

806
00:30:01,680 --> 00:30:03,359
Have you contacted her family?

807
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:04,480
Not yet.

808
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:05,919
But the plaintiff's lawyer said

809
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:08,679
the child's grandmother
lives in Jinshuli Community.

810
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:09,919
I plan to go there

811
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:11,680
and hand the child over to her.

812
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:12,919
That works.

813
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:14,879
A child this young being with strangers

814
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,239
won't feel at ease.

815
00:30:16,240 --> 00:30:17,920
It's better if we can find family.

816
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:19,239
Take my car later,

817
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:20,159
and bring someone with you.

818
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,039
Who's around?

819
00:30:21,040 --> 00:30:21,999
Is Xiang Hui here?

820
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,920
Xiang Hui went to the hospital too.

821
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:25,959
Only the plaintiff's lawyer
knows the address.

822
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:27,800
- I was thinking of asking her to take me.
- That's fine.

823
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:30,160
A woman will handle
the child more easily.

824
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:33,319
Alright, go.

825
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:34,360
No need.

826
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:36,399
That address isn't far from my home.

827
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:37,319
It's convenient for me.

828
00:30:37,320 --> 00:30:38,880
I'll just take a taxi.

829
00:30:39,080 --> 00:30:41,439
Alright then,
take good care of the child.

830
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:43,159
Report to me anytime
if something comes up.

831
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:43,970
Okay.

832
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,640
Shen, wait.

833
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:52,199
Take this child seat.

834
00:30:52,200 --> 00:30:53,559
Don't let the child get hurt on the way.

835
00:30:53,560 --> 00:30:54,279
Okay.

836
00:30:54,280 --> 00:30:55,300
Stay safe.

837
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:04,679
Judge Shen,

838
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:06,400
your court is well prepared,

839
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:08,239
even has child seats.

840
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,519
You should thank your

841
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:11,040
excellent litigants.

842
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:12,719
In Jing's office,

843
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:14,839
there are still half a dozen diapers

844
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:17,120
and a can of stage-three formula.

845
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:20,280
That's quite touching.

846
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:22,520
People's judges serve the people.

847
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:24,079
You're impressive too,

848
00:31:24,080 --> 00:31:25,919
giving up your personal time

849
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:27,440
to help me look for someone.

850
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,479
Judge Shen,

851
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:30,199
this isn't my personal time.

852
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:32,319
I had a client meeting scheduled,

853
00:31:32,320 --> 00:31:34,920
a contract dispute worth a million.

854
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:36,279
Now I'm out here

855
00:31:36,280 --> 00:31:37,399
with you,

856
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:40,000
that deal is probably gone.

857
00:31:40,640 --> 00:31:41,920
Sorry.

858
00:31:44,840 --> 00:31:47,600
Judge Shen, I didn't mean it like that.

859
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:49,599
I'm still a legal professional

860
00:31:49,600 --> 00:31:52,960
with conscience and compassion.

861
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,599
I owe you a favor.

862
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:56,999
If there's a chance,

863
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,450
I'll repay it.

864
00:31:58,640 --> 00:31:59,920
There's a chance.

865
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,199
Judge Shen,

866
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,359
about the

867
00:32:02,360 --> 00:32:03,879
Liu Lihua case I mentioned before,

868
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:05,679
could you not grant the divorce?

869
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:07,309
My client really doesn't want one.

870
00:32:07,310 --> 00:32:08,480
No.

871
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:09,599
I will repay the favor

872
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:11,680
at the right time.

873
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:12,999
But remember,

874
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:13,919
never try

875
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:16,520
to trade work matters with me.

876
00:32:17,080 --> 00:32:19,240
How is that a trade?

877
00:32:19,520 --> 00:32:20,800
I was

878
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,960
just appealing for consideration.

879
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:34,960
Which building is it?

880
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:40,320
Probably that one.

881
00:32:56,040 --> 00:32:57,199
Do you

882
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,839
recognize which building?

883
00:32:58,840 --> 00:33:01,599
I only glanced out the window back then,

884
00:33:01,600 --> 00:33:03,680
didn't realize there were
so many identical ones.

885
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:06,519
Xiaolongbao,

886
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:08,480
do you remember which building
your grandma lives in?

887
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:10,639
You don't remember?

888
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:11,639
Maybe

889
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:13,440
we should check
with property management.

890
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:14,719
You should at least know

891
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:16,640
Liu Wenbo's mother's name, right?

892
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:20,559
(Owner and tenant list)

893
00:33:20,560 --> 00:33:21,959
I'm really sorry, Judge Shen.

894
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:23,360
I checked again.

895
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:25,159
She's not on

896
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,440
either list.

897
00:33:27,120 --> 00:33:28,599
That's impossible.

898
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:30,039
The last time I came here

899
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:31,520
was just about a month ago.

900
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:34,319
His son even
came downstairs in slippers.

901
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:35,519
You see,

902
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:36,799
there's no way

903
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:38,519
the elderly woman would move

904
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:40,079
in such a short time, right?

905
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:41,319
I understand, Miss,

906
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:43,279
but these are resettlement apartments.

907
00:33:43,280 --> 00:33:45,279
Some transactions
can't be transferred yet.

908
00:33:45,280 --> 00:33:46,239
The new owners

909
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,920
won't be in our system.

910
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:50,279
If the place is rented,

911
00:33:50,280 --> 00:33:51,559
that's even harder to trace.

912
00:33:51,560 --> 00:33:52,359
Look,

913
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:54,399
this child is an internet personality,

914
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:56,000
very popular.

915
00:33:56,040 --> 00:33:57,760
Have you seen her?

916
00:33:58,280 --> 00:33:59,239
Sorry,

917
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:00,879
I don't go online much.

918
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:02,159
I can't recognize her.

919
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:02,890
You...

920
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:04,719
Why don't you go online?

921
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:05,720
Forget it.

922
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,519
Sorry to trouble you, thank you.

923
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:08,039
It's fine.

924
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:08,799
Let's go.

925
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:10,280
Come on, Xiaolongbao.

926
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:11,380
Let's go.

927
00:34:11,720 --> 00:34:12,680
No.

928
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:20,639
I'm sorry, Judge Shen.

929
00:34:20,640 --> 00:34:21,839
Back then,

930
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:22,919
I just glanced

931
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:24,319
out the window.

932
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:26,759
Didn't expect
so many identical buildings.

933
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:28,680
It's fine, it's not your fault.

934
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:33,000
So what now?

935
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,600
Where do we go?

936
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:37,280
Back to court?

937
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:43,320
Why is Xiaolongbao crying?

938
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,119
Don't cry.

939
00:34:45,120 --> 00:34:47,560
- We won't go back to court, we won't.
- Not going back.

940
00:34:47,680 --> 00:34:49,280
Don't cry, sweetheart.

941
00:34:55,080 --> 00:34:56,239
Xiaolongbao,

942
00:34:56,240 --> 00:34:57,599
are you hungry?

943
00:34:57,600 --> 00:34:59,410
I will take you
to get something tasty, okay?

944
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:02,199
So you're hungry.

945
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:03,800
Then let's go eat.

946
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:05,080
Let's go.

947
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:09,119
What should we eat?

948
00:35:09,120 --> 00:35:11,280
Big buns or little buns?

949
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:18,440
This way, please.

950
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:21,479
For this meal,

951
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:23,199
what's the court reimbursement standard?

952
00:35:23,200 --> 00:35:23,959
No reimbursement.

953
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:25,039
Didn't I owe you a favor?

954
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:26,150
Consider it repaid.

955
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:29,120
No need to make it this formal.

956
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:31,599
Even though
I did lose quite a bit tonight,

957
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:33,640
I can't have you pay personally.

958
00:35:34,520 --> 00:35:35,279
Besides,

959
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:37,319
what I said about owing a favor,

960
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:38,919
I was joking.

961
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:39,759
Don't worry,

962
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:41,269
I won't bring up

963
00:35:41,270 --> 00:35:42,680
Liu Lihua's case again.

964
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:45,079
And,

965
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:47,199
as her father's former lawyer,

966
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:48,399
even if you didn't ask,

967
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:50,560
I would still take care of the child.

968
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:53,200
Let's switch to another place.

969
00:35:53,240 --> 00:35:54,390
You're not hungry?

970
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:56,639
Even if you're not,

971
00:35:56,640 --> 00:35:58,279
your former client's child is.

972
00:35:58,280 --> 00:35:59,319
Let's go, Xiaolongbao.

973
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,600
Let's get something good.

974
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:04,040
Slow down.

975
00:36:07,640 --> 00:36:09,919
Buffet. We have three options,

976
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:12,239
single, double, and family set.

977
00:36:12,240 --> 00:36:13,070
I won't eat.

978
00:36:14,200 --> 00:36:14,959
Alright.

979
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:16,759
The family set includes all dishes,

980
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:18,360
and a gift for the child.

981
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:19,839
Okay, thank you.

982
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:21,639
Please add a child's utensil set.

983
00:36:21,640 --> 00:36:23,320
Alright, please wait a moment.

984
00:36:25,680 --> 00:36:27,039
I'm really not that hungry.

985
00:36:27,040 --> 00:36:29,520
Since we're here,

986
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:33,460
just eat.

987
00:36:51,880 --> 00:36:54,679
(Observation Room)

988
00:36:54,680 --> 00:36:55,639
Judge Shen,

989
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:56,980
how is Le?

990
00:36:57,290 --> 00:36:58,679
She's fine, it's under control now.

991
00:36:58,680 --> 00:36:59,839
Ma Da went to pay,

992
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:01,480
and I'm staying with her.

993
00:37:01,680 --> 00:37:02,960
What happened?

994
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:05,399
It's nothing,
just improper medication use...

995
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:06,600
That scared me.

996
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:08,759
Fortunately, it's not a miscarriage,

997
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:10,239
just an overdose.

998
00:37:10,240 --> 00:37:12,039
Go check on Le, I'll make a call.

999
00:37:12,040 --> 00:37:13,320
Alright.

1000
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:15,839
It's fine, Judge Shen,

1001
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:16,919
everything's under control.

1002
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:19,359
Le's husband is on his way back.

1003
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,639
How are things on your side?

1004
00:37:20,640 --> 00:37:21,849
I heard from Xiang Hui

1005
00:37:21,850 --> 00:37:23,839
you went to find the grandmother
with Xiaolongbao.

1006
00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:24,999
No.

1007
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:25,959
I was going to ask

1008
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,199
when you and Ma Da would be back,

1009
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:28,340
but forget it.

1010
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:29,279
Alright.

1011
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:31,560
Let's stay in touch.

1012
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:37,840
You peel this part off,

1013
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:40,359
like taking off a shirt,

1014
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:42,199
remove the shell like this.

1015
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:43,010
See?

1016
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:44,720
All peeled.

1017
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,080
Got it?

1018
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:49,240
She's so young,
how could she learn that?

1019
00:37:49,680 --> 00:37:50,719
With this time,

1020
00:37:50,720 --> 00:37:52,239
you could peel a few more for her.

1021
00:37:52,240 --> 00:37:53,639
Why not?

1022
00:37:53,640 --> 00:37:55,880
I could make dumplings when I was four.

1023
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:57,519
Come on, Xiaolongbao,

1024
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:59,200
try peeling one yourself.

1025
00:38:00,720 --> 00:38:02,600
Xiaolongbao, listen to me.

1026
00:38:02,720 --> 00:38:04,519
You can't choose your parents.

1027
00:38:04,520 --> 00:38:05,999
If they're unreliable,

1028
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:08,680
you have to rely on yourself
and grow stronger.

1029
00:38:08,720 --> 00:38:09,780
Understand?

1030
00:38:10,520 --> 00:38:11,719
Trust me.

1031
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:14,200
Kids have unlimited potential.

1032
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:16,720
Try it yourself.

1033
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:25,479
Try the sashimi,

1034
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:27,160
it's fresh, a specialty.

1035
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:28,360
I don't eat that.

1036
00:38:29,040 --> 00:38:30,880
I never eat raw food.

1037
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:32,879
A client once told me

1038
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:35,800
you can get parasites from it.

1039
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:42,159
That client probably
went to a bad place.

1040
00:38:42,160 --> 00:38:43,679
This one is fine.

1041
00:38:43,680 --> 00:38:45,999
You won't know until you try.

1042
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:48,240
At least then you'll
have the right to judge.

1043
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,600
Alright,

1044
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,479
can't let it go to waste.

1045
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:59,360
Pick something less scary.

1046
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:04,640
Dip it in sauce.

1047
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:18,510
How is it?

1048
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,719
Not that scary.

1049
00:39:20,720 --> 00:39:22,800
Have more, order more if needed.

1050
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:28,160
I'll try the pink one.

1051
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:37,760
This one's good.

1052
00:39:39,120 --> 00:39:41,040
Same as usual, take a look.

1053
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:43,039
Li, your lamb is amazing.

1054
00:39:43,040 --> 00:39:44,279
Absolutely

1055
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:45,270
top-notch.

1056
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,559
Of course.

1057
00:39:46,560 --> 00:39:47,330
Good.

1058
00:39:51,200 --> 00:39:52,350
(Li Tan Lamb)
Fei,

1059
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:54,320
no more homework, we're going home.

1060
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:55,930
Here.

1061
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:59,399
Alright, take it.

1062
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:00,359
Drive safe on the way back.

1063
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,230
Got it.

1064
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:06,759
Let me help, thank you.

1065
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:08,150
Let's go, heading home.

1066
00:40:11,050 --> 00:40:12,600
Come on, get in the car.

1067
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:15,190
Wait.

1068
00:40:15,590 --> 00:40:17,359
Mom has a lot of missed calls.

1069
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,800
What's going on?

1070
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:25,080
Why did you just call back?

1071
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:31,039
I was at Li's place,

1072
00:40:31,040 --> 00:40:32,559
no signal. What's wrong?

1073
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,730
Fei's location
still shows she's at the park.

1074
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,400
Fei is with me.

1075
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:39,439
With you? What happened?

1076
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:41,079
I picked her up,

1077
00:40:41,080 --> 00:40:42,279
then came to Li's place.

1078
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,639
I've been in the cold storage,

1079
00:40:43,640 --> 00:40:45,599
no signal the whole time.

1080
00:40:45,600 --> 00:40:47,000
At Li's shop?

1081
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:49,200
Wait.

1082
00:40:52,680 --> 00:40:53,520
Here.

1083
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:55,320
See?

1084
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:56,199
Fei,

1085
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:57,439
say hi to Mom.

1086
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:59,319
Mom, you've been working hard.

1087
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:01,240
Fei.

1088
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:11,039
Feel better now?

1089
00:41:11,040 --> 00:41:12,919
Why is her location still at the park?

1090
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:14,110
Where's her watch?

1091
00:41:14,240 --> 00:41:16,640
She's wearing it, of course.

1092
00:41:17,120 --> 00:41:19,400
Show Mom your watch.

1093
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:24,120
Where is it?

1094
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:31,759
Fei's watch

1095
00:41:31,760 --> 00:41:33,239
might have fallen at the park.

1096
00:41:33,240 --> 00:41:34,319
I'll let the teacher know

1097
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,839
and have them contact

1098
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,319
the park management

1099
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,359
to see if it can be found.

1100
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,439
Forget it.

1101
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:40,800
As long as she's safe.

1102
00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:51,550
Fei,

1103
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:54,359
did the strap come loose,

1104
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:55,559
or did you take it off

1105
00:41:55,560 --> 00:41:57,000
when washing your hands?

1106
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:01,239
It's okay.

1107
00:42:01,240 --> 00:42:02,159
If it's lost,

1108
00:42:02,160 --> 00:42:04,039
Dad will buy you a new one.

1109
00:42:04,040 --> 00:42:04,910
Okay?

1110
00:42:05,320 --> 00:42:06,399
Today

1111
00:42:06,400 --> 00:42:07,599
was Dad's fault.

1112
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:08,679
I stayed in the cold storage

1113
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:09,839
too long,

1114
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:10,959
no signal,

1115
00:42:10,960 --> 00:42:12,599
missed Mom's calls

1116
00:42:12,600 --> 00:42:13,880
and made her worry.

1117
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:14,639
But now

1118
00:42:14,640 --> 00:42:16,119
I've explained everything to Mom,

1119
00:42:16,120 --> 00:42:17,190
right?

1120
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:20,880
So don't worry.

1121
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:22,790
Good girl.

1122
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:24,399
Get in the car.

1123
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:26,640
Take your schoolbag.

1124
00:42:26,680 --> 00:42:28,960
Stay in the car, I'll move the goods.

1125
00:42:35,440 --> 00:42:36,730
So what now?

1126
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:39,200
We've finished eating,
Xiaolongbao is sleepy.

1127
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:41,160
We're heading back to court?

1128
00:42:49,120 --> 00:42:50,759
Ms. Shu, how is it?

1129
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:51,799
Did you find the child?

1130
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:53,639
Yes, she's fine.

1131
00:42:53,640 --> 00:42:55,520
That's good. Where are you?

1132
00:42:55,560 --> 00:42:57,039
I'm still in Dongshan District.

1133
00:42:57,040 --> 00:42:58,240
Dongshan?

1134
00:42:59,280 --> 00:43:00,839
Why are you still at Forest Park?

1135
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:02,440
I'll explain later.

1136
00:43:02,480 --> 00:43:04,080
How is Xiaolongbao?

1137
00:43:14,620 --> 00:43:18,080
♪All the little things
between you and me♪

1138
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:20,760
♪Woven into our lives♪

1139
00:43:21,610 --> 00:43:23,590
♪The building blocks of life♪

1140
00:43:23,590 --> 00:43:25,290
♪Shape the sky above us♪

1141
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:27,450
♪Are you doing alright?♪

1142
00:43:27,770 --> 00:43:30,450
♪What are you struggling for?♪

1143
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:35,150
♪Some questions weigh like mountains♪

1144
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:40,380
♪How do we piece life back together?♪

1145
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:45,130
♪So hate can fade
and love feels new again♪

1146
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:48,200
♪Reclaim the barren parts of life♪

1147
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:54,570
♪Walking this road
together, still hoping♪

1148
00:43:55,360 --> 00:44:00,420
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

1149
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:04,690
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

1150
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:09,900
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

1151
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Where fairness stands♪

1152
00:44:15,350 --> 00:44:17,590
♪Within every heart♪

1153
00:44:17,590 --> 00:44:20,240
♪So many voices calling♪

1154
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:24,790
♪Struggling, lost,
waiting for an answer♪

1155
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:27,140
♪Light up the lamps♪

1156
00:44:27,140 --> 00:44:29,810
♪To answer those voices♪

1157
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:32,240
♪You deserve to be happy♪

1158
